.058824 .098039 .137255 rg
BT 1 0 0 1 0 54.5 Tm /F1 9.5 Tf 16 TL .21826 Tw (A system may correctly authenticate a user and still execute actions that are not justified at the moment they) Tj T* 0 Tw 2.199279 Tw (occur. The authentication was successful. The session is valid. The identity is confirmed. None of this) Tj T* 0 Tw .121945 Tw (establishes that the specific action now being initiated carries valid authority. Legitimacy is not determined by) Tj T* 0 Tw (successful login. It is determined by valid authority at execution.) Tj T* ET
Q
