BT 1 0 0 1 0 54.5 Tm /F1 9.5 Tf 16 TL .966179 Tw (A system can therefore be secure at entry while operating without authority during execution. The security) Tj T* 0 Tw .155512 Tw (infrastructure is intact. The authentication records are clean. The access logs show nothing unusual. And the) Tj T* 0 Tw .507942 Tw (system continues to take actions that were never legitimately authorised \227 because the control mechanism) Tj T* 0 Tw (that would prevent them was never part of the security model to begin with.) Tj T* ET
